folder: Greenwich Street & Desbrosses Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Greenwich Street, east side, at Desbrosses Street, showing the express and uptown platforms and the tracks of the 9th Avenue Elevated Line. The photographer is on the downtown platform to photograph this panoramic view.

June 7, 1940
Views 1,2

P. L. Sperr

folder: Desbrosses Street & Greenwich Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
(1) Desbrosses Street, south side northwest corner of Greenwich Street, showing piers of elevated after demolition, looking westwards.

June 1941.

(2) Same, different angle,

P.L.Speer.

May 5, 1941.
